{"tid":1991120,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"衰遠必豬！支那大使威脅澳洲 若不停止支那肺炎調查 後果自負！","createTime":"2020-04-27T08:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T08:35:39.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"07f2f3c385b69e63994fd26c8e93d2617c3747ad","tid":1991120,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:17:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.tr.news/china-threatens-australia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tr.news%2Fchina-threatens-australia%2F&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4Qp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=b71f4940\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.tr.news/china-threatens-australia/</a><br />\n<br />\n早前，澳洲政府呼籲進行獨立調查中國肺炎的來源與處置情形，遭到了中國駐澳洲大使Cheng Jingye(成競業)威脅，若是澳洲不停止對中國肺炎追根究底的行為，可能會遭受到嚴重的經濟後果。這可能會引發中國的抵制行為。<br />\n <br />\n對此澳洲外交部長Marie Payne表示：<br />\n <br />\n澳洲已經原則性地呼籲對COVID-19爆發的罕見全球危機進行獨立調查，這一危機對健康，經濟與社會造成嚴重影響。<br />\n <br />\n當我們需要的是全球合作時，我們拒絕任何認為經濟脅迫是對於這種評估的恰當回應。<br />\n <br />\n對於中國的霸凌行為，許多澳洲非中國裔網友都十分火大<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/OzraeliAvi/status/1254636193309814785?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FOzraeliAvi%2Fstatus%2F1254636193309814785%3Fs%3D19&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4Qp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=2d58dbb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FOzraeliAvi%2Fstatus%2F1254636193309814785%3Fs%3D19&h=d0ca4da7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/OzraeliAvi/status/1254636193309814785?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"b7fec36b7acfdbdaba5c1c65695ab27824b33d69","tid":1991120,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"真係好撚 MAN, 全世界屬於強國真係好合理架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}